text: @UPSHelp So my iPhone was supposed to be delivered yday but I saw no door tag nor anyone in my security cam footage try to deliver. Now it’s supposedly out right now but I’m concerned because it still ain’t here. I reaaaallllly need my iPhone today, guys. Wassup?
